{"tid":1556493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《人神共憤》今日黑警阻礙救援自殺手足","createTime":"2019-09-09T18:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T23:29:57.000Z","uid":204481,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"02a102e5765009bedaa6f47c93234637895b4163","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"今日秀茂坪區有手足留遺書想輕生<br />\n即時有大量手足洗樓並發現自殺手足反鎖係屋企唔肯開門 <span style=\"color: red;\">並有手足朋友、社區主任安撫緊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">消防 救護亦到場支援</span><br />\n<br />\n但10分鐘後1便衣2藍衫狗到場 我以請求嘅語氣向狗表示「唔該阿sir可唔可以唔過去住，<span style=\"color: red;\">個女仔表示驚警察</span>。」而一名便衣警員推開我繼續走到門口<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後白衫狗到場 我同樣以請求態度向白衫說明情況 白衫狗表示「<span style=\"color: red;\">我 In charge 。</span>」 之後強行衝到消防救護之中。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁烈士跳落黎嘅原因 我開始明白 <span style=\"color: red;\">狗不顧一切刺激手足情緒</span><br />\n<br />\n最後手足唔好再做傻豬豬 死係解決唔到任何問題 只會令同路人傷心</span>"},{"pid":"b235f860dbdba16e0d90c0e4be1bc3b6342fe18f","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"efeb76488d43ff4d94212bad6f0143f9956c1fca","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"65a117e4e3fc10a72f32e217fb02d5e7fdca03f7","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"f0f7edea96c7e5d8343d9d2e43a79a5fc65fd277","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"0d5430e777b11d63c4e31601426be28830a65a66","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:05:37.000Z","msg":"5/20"},{"pid":"3fa0cbec6e03c63c50a3f908180cbef53773ab33","tid":1556493,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"6/20"},{"pid":"19774bf42fe1baf8